org.sql: SELECT time_entries.* FROM time_entries INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = time_entries.project_id WHERE time_entries.issue_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'time_tracking') IS NOT NULL
